c selfishness in all He wrote seeing all men have this corruption in them God in his wisdom saw another course fitter for In other words according to Westbrook Bradford found private enterprise to be the most suitable economic policy for mankind in its fallen Let's not make the same mistake that the Pilgrims Private property allows a society to flourish the alternative brings starvation poverty and Paul Schmidt Advocates for Self Government Davy Crockett Chapter President Judith Drive Johnson City TN uunet Freedom seems to have unleashed the creative energies of the people and leads to ever higher levels of income and social report